      "anchor_id": "issue-gothrumedia-gothru-api-new-1299",
      "display_title": "Issue #1299: API Get Panorama Manual Blur",
      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Description</h2>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"images/image-7e87caa6-d72f-46d2-97d8-9973e9e3d5a9.png\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1266\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"images/image-7e87caa6-d72f-46d2-97d8-9973e9e3d5a9.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 1266px;; aspect-ratio: 1920 / 1266; background-color: var(--bgColor-muted); border-radius: 6px\" class=\"js-gh-image-fallback\"></a>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Alongside the backend fixes for the blur processing, several UI updates are required on the <strong>Blur section</strong> interface (Anonymize 360 Images) to improve usability and remove non-functional features.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Sub-tasks</h2>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Completed task\" checked=\"\"> Backend API ready: <code class=\"notranslate\">GET /panoramas/manual-blur/{mid}</code> returns <code class=\"notranslate\">{ panos: [{ pano_id, blur_count }] }</code> (panos without blur omitted) for the indicator.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo from Developer</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Backend endpoint for the manual-blur indicator is implemented and merged to <code class=\"notranslate\">main</code>.</p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">GET /panoramas/manual-blur/{mid}</code></li>\n<li><strong>Auth:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">auth</code> middleware (raw token in <code class=\"notranslate\">Authorization</code> header, no <code class=\"notranslate\">Bearer</code> prefix) + moderation-ownership check.</li>\n<li><strong>Behavior:</strong> Reads the <code class=\"notranslate\">8_blooring</code> table and returns, per panorama, the number of manual-blur regions. Panoramas without blur are omitted.</li>\n<li><strong>Response (decrypted):</strong>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-json notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"{\n  &quot;messages&quot;: &quot;Data retrieved successfully.&quot;,\n  &quot;panos&quot;: [\n    { &quot;pano_id&quot;: 12, &quot;blur_count&quot;: 3 },\n    { &quot;pano_id&quot;: 18, &quot;blur_count&quot;: 1 }\n  ]\n}\"><pre class=\"notranslate\">{\n  <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"messages\"</span>: <span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span>Data retrieved successfully.<span class=\"pl-pds\">\"</span></span>,\n  <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"panos\"</span>: [\n    { <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"pano_id\"</span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">12</span>, <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"blur_count\"</span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">3</span> },\n    { <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"pano_id\"</span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">18</span>, <span class=\"pl-ent\">\"blur_count\"</span>: <span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span> }\n  ]\n}</pre></div>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Errors:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">409 TOURS.MODERATION_NOT_OWNER</code> (not owner / not found), <code class=\"notranslate\">401</code> (missing/invalid token).</li>\n<li><strong>Architecture:</strong> Strict ADR (Controller → Action → DTO → Repository) in the <code class=\"notranslate\">Panoramas</code> domain; encrypted response envelope.</li>\n<li><strong>Docs:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/v2/panoramas/get-manual-blur.md</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">ADR_MIGRATED_APIS.md</code> (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1641732385\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/GoThru-API-New/issues/30\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/GoThru-API-New/issues/30/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/GoThru-API-New/issues/30\">#30</a>).</li>\n</ul>",
