      "display_title": "Issue #1302: Update API Get Photographers",
      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Description</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Add a new <strong><code class=\"notranslate\">status</code></strong> query parameter to the Get Photographers dashboard API and forward it to the photographer service.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Endpoint:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">/v1/photographers/users/dashboard</code><br>\n<strong>Controller action:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">app/Http/Controllers/Photographers/Support/Action/RequestFeaturedUser.php</code></p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Change</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Read <code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> from the request query and include it in the params forwarded to <code class=\"notranslate\">BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"$search = $request-&gt;query('search');\n$filter = $request-&gt;query('filter');\n$status = $request-&gt;query('status');\n$size   = $request-&gt;query('size');\n$page   = $request-&gt;query('page');\n\n$url = env(&quot;BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER&quot;) . &quot;/v1/photographers/users/dashboard&quot;;\n$params = [\n    'search' =&gt; $search,\n    'filter' =&gt; $filter,\n    'status' =&gt; $status,\n    'size'   =&gt; $size,\n    'page'   =&gt; $page,\n];\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>search</span> = <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>request</span>-&gt;<span class=\"pl-en\">query</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">search</span>'</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>filter</span> = <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>request</span>-&gt;<span class=\"pl-en\">query</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">filter</span>'</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>status</span> = <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>request</span>-&gt;<span class=\"pl-en\">query</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">status</span>'</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>size</span>   = <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>request</span>-&gt;<span class=\"pl-en\">query</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">size</span>'</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>page</span>   = <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>request</span>-&gt;<span class=\"pl-en\">query</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">page</span>'</span>);\n\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>url</span> = <span class=\"pl-en\">env</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">\"<span class=\"pl-s\">BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER</span>\"</span>) . <span class=\"pl-s\">\"<span class=\"pl-s\">/v1/photographers/users/dashboard</span>\"</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>params</span> = [\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">search</span>'</span> =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>search</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">filter</span>'</span> =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>filter</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">status</span>'</span> =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>status</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">size</span>'</span>   =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>size</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">page</span>'</span>   =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>page</span>,\n];</pre></div>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance Criteria</h2>\n<ol dir=\"auto\">\n<li>The <code class=\"notranslate\">/v1/photographers/users/dashboard</code> endpoint accepts a <code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> query param and forwards it to the photographer service.</li>\n<li>Existing params (<code class=\"notranslate\">search</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">filter</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">size</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">page</code>) keep working — no regression.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo from Developer</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Summary of work:</strong></p>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Added new <code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> query parameter to <code class=\"notranslate\">RequestFeaturedUser</code> action.</li>\n<li><code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> is read via <code class=\"notranslate\">$request-&gt;query('status')</code>.</li>\n<li>Forwarded <code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> in the <code class=\"notranslate\">$params</code> array sent to <code class=\"notranslate\">BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER</code> at <code class=\"notranslate\">/v1/photographers/users/dashboard</code>.</li>\n<li>No changes to existing params (<code class=\"notranslate\">search</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">filter</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">size</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">page</code>) — backward compatible.</li>\n</ul>",
